      "description": "*ACTUALLY* FUN EVENT PAGES (100% FREE)\n\n- Create pages for any event — birthdays, pregames, kickbacks, dinners, date nights, game nights, watch parties, pickup games, group trips, bachelor/bachelorettes, weddings, and more\n- Make it aesthetic with page themes, effects, and event posters—or upload your own\n- Guests can see who else is going and add comments, GIFs, and photos to the page\n\nINVITE FRIENDS ON ANY PLATFORM (not just iPhones)\n\n- Customize your RSVP settings for all types of events, public or private\n- Invite anyone with a link — *guests don’t need the app*! One link to send invites to both Apple and Non-Apple users, and you can track RSVPs in real time.\n- Re-use your guest lists for future events, and invite people you meet at other Partiful parties\n\nSHARE UPDATES AND PHOTOS\n\n- Text Blast your guests with important updates\n- Post comments on the page that guests can react and reply to\n- Upload pics to a Shared Photo Album, and collect photos from guests\n\nFIND A TIME THAT WORKS FOR EVERYONE\n\n- Not sure who’s free? Poll your guests before selecting a final date\n- Guests can RSVP to multiple options, and you pick what works best\n- Everyone’s RSVP is automatically updated once you pick a date\n\nBE TYPE-A ABOUT IT\n\n- Drop your Venmo or CashApp for guests to chip in\n- Limit spots available, we’ll handle the waitlist\n- Add a questionnaire to collect dietary restrictions, location preferences, and more\n\nOR BE CHILL\n\n- Create a simple page in *seconds* (literally)\n- Leave date & time TBD, figure out details later\n- Keep it casual with designs for board game nights, dinners, and date night\n\nKEEP TRACK OF YOUR SOCIAL LIFE\n\n- View events you’re planning and attending in one place\n- Automatically add all Partiful events to your Google, Apple, or Outlook calendar\n- Check the guest lists to see who’s coming\n- Discover Open Invite events hosted by your Mutuals\n\nORGANIZER PROFILES\n\n- Showcase all your events with a single shareable link\n- Easily re-invite past guests and grow a community that keeps showing up\n- Work with co-admins to create and manage events\n\nPARTY PROFILES\n\n- Add a bio, profile photo, and your socials\n- Show off how many events you’ve hosted and attended\n- Keep track of your Mutuals (the people you’ve partied with)\n\n……\n\nGot questions, suggestions, or fun party ideas? DM us on IG @partiful or email us at hello@partiful.com\n\n:) Follow us on TikTok, Instagram, and Twitter @partiful",
